_sText:
Remade/Extended Dust2

Credits:
Valve - Map Maker
lilBernie - Inspiration of remaking map, almost making it a CS:S version of the Dust3 of lilBernie.

Since Beta 3.5, nav files are now included.
Current Version: Beta 3.5

Changelogs:
 Beta 3.2
Added new way from middle > T-Tunnel
Added crate to the left side of t spawn.

Beta 3.3
Fixed the wall not properly sealed on other way of double doors to near t-spawn
Changed position of crate near t-spawn to fix an issue causing black wall behind it.

Beta 3.4
Replaced the roof texture to different concrete texture to fix an missing texture issue. [Thanks Frikadellendieb]

Beta 3.5
Now actually fixed the missing texture issue.

Information:

This map is a remade/remaked dust2 to fix some bomb-stuck places and extending its look and experience.

Also includes some inspiration from lilBernie's Dust3 for CSGO: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=710746137
